{"tid":370611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"未來教師帶同結他到尖沙咀碼頭追風","createTime":"2017-08-23T06:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T12:22:24.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5949d45420993c67e15063901c0cdbb1823d690","tid":370611,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/142915_a04ed5240d716d6949a831370ea936a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F142915_a04ed5240d716d6949a831370ea936a1.jpg&h=d0505efd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天文台清晨5時20分懸掛8號風球，市區風力開始較強，香港教育大學3男1女生帶同結他，結伴到尖沙嘴碼頭追風，但風力未算強勁。眾人表示第一次追風，原以為會有點風，豈料沒有，唯有唱下歌，「以前睇電視，見到的人會比風吹郁架。」"},{"pid":"ef45714bea706086f950f6d5bcf353fcb83e9f6a","tid":370611,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:31:26.000Z","msg":"兵"},{"pid":"47d26014092e645c3c4ec8e13262127b511b7db1","tid":370611,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:33:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兵</blockquote><br />\n咁既樣都有兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558c9650695a4f77cd89551fd61917520fb82993","tid":370611,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兵</blockquote><br />\n咁既樣都有兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你又睇下啲兵咩樣"}]}